version_description:
- Search for brands or categories via Spotlight.
- Bug fixes and performance improvements.

- 3D touch items on product listings to see outfit view of each product.
- Bug fixes and performance improvements.

- Log in with a fingerprint using Touch ID.
- Bug fixes and performance improvements.

- You can now use 1Password to help you log in.
- Bug fixes and performance improvements.

Our biggest update yet, we've refreshed and reengineered the END. app from the ground up. In this version:

- Save items for later: You can now save items to purchase later, as well as create and name multiple lists. If you already have saved lists from the END. website, they will automatically sync
- Intuitive navigation: We've introduced a user-friendly tab bar for easy access to your account and saved items
- Smoother checkout: Simpler, streamlined ordering including payment with just a touch using Apple Pay

It's never been faster and easier to browse and buy our world-renowned range of influential brands, plus there are more features and improvements on the way.

Introducing END. Launches for iOS: browse the destination for high heat sneaker releases and submit your draw entries directly in the END. app.

- See all upcoming and past END. Launches releases

In this update we've made it even easier and faster to checkout with Apple Pay.

- Skip lengthy address forms and choose your address from Apple Pay
- See your shipping method and all relevant order information within Apple Pay
- Bug fixes and performance improvements

In this update we've made it really easy to input your shipping or billing address so you can checkout even quicker.

- Start typing your address and we'll suggest addresses so you don't need to type it all
- Tap "Use my location" for suggested addresses based on where you are
- Bug fixes and performance improvements

- On product listings you can now filter products by price.
